{
  "stem": "23579.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were given a piece of bread a day because people, they went to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the Germans was giving them a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know, but a small piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on this bread, they were living.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had power of death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Germans tell them that we need, today, 50 people to go to work, they knew right away that is for dead, but they have to give it to them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave it to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They have to give it to them, the 50 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said for work, but they took them, and they were killing them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later, we knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish population?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They hate them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hate them because they took away their families.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Families, they took away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You take away the head of the family, so the whole family is going down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Judenrat didn't have nothing to do with that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They told them you have to give me 50, 100 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, my friends, Daniel [INAUDIBLE] and [INAUDIBLE], we studied together in gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was only 3% Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were the head of the Judenrat because I was studying French.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were studying German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this ghetto, I was-- this was in December 1941 till April '42.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "April 15, '42.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had doctors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't have nothing for the sick, to give.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have medicine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were dying, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Listen, better die than to be killed like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this was a war, a terrible war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A war of survival.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you could survive yourself, you didn't give a hoot for nobody else.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
